      Notifies when the user parked.

      Notifies when user physical activity changes.
      Get the activity type by calling BrainsAPI.ActivityRecognition.getActivityType(intent)
      Get the activity confidence by calling BrainsAPI.ActivityRecognition.getActivityConfidence(intent)
      Get the activity type string by calling BrainsAPI.ActivityRecognition.getActivityString(intent)
      The specific events that can be received under this action are listed under prefix of USER_ACTIVITY_EVENT_
